{"id": 2899, "genre": 1000, "title": "你是哪种类型的“互联网人质”？", "description": "你觉得互联网产品都为你设置了哪些“小陷阱”？欢迎在评论区补充。（题图来自：iStock ©️ jossdim）", "record_count": 7537, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190418113450qZo9bOfBwWFiARMn.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-22T17:00:36Z", "questions": [{"id": 5685, "title": "你是哪种类型的“互联网人质”？", "content": "你是哪种类型的“互联网人质”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 339310, "content": "订阅型人质，订阅容易退订难", "image": "img/option/option/20190415164128BWa5U0n274rsRg8I.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 339311, "content": "更新型人质，避免软件、系统的频繁催促，自己先主动更新", "image": "img/option/option/20190415164543uBAn8RtTfvUorQ9L.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 339313, "content": "回复型人质，别人发的消息/评论不回复很难受", "image": "img/option/option/20190415164824IEe7lypmCrqAXUOZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 339314, "content": "撤回型人质，有错别字的消息一定要撤回修改", "image": "img/option/option/20190415165109AIksCaWt3b6Dr2nJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 339316, "content": "已读型人质，要把所有“未读消息”点成已读才舒服", "image": "img/option/option/20190415165250y2J7KBdbl9wUOmGC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 339318, "content": "分享型人质，做了的事情没分享好像白做了一样", "image": "img/option/option/201904151655343eXWYEnLNupFPK4I.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 339321, "content": "凑单型人质，为了满减买了不需要的东西", "image": "img/option/option/20190415165847VesPlcjYDbto0w6Q.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 339326, "content": "好评型人质，评论区有一定比例的好评才敢下单", "image": "img/option/option/20190415170041arQ1bRLmNIHA7x0w.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 339331, "content": "都不是，从不会被套路绑架", "image": "img/option/option/20190415170303mcaSFguUzIjl8yT1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}